This is a CMake project to build it run

  $ mkdir build
  $ cd build
  $ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ../
	$ make all
	$ make install		 (optional)

the project needs:

	>= g++ 4.7
	>= boost 1.53
	>= gnutls 3.1.10 // not released yet
	>= gpgme more or less recent version
	>= idn2 more or less recent version
	>= gpg installed

boost 1.53 is included
gnutls 3.1.10 (patched) is included

to use it call

	$ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DUSE_INTERNAL_GNUTLS=ON -DUSE_INTERNAL_BOOST=ON ../

build on fedora 19. and possible other recent linux versions.

